looka (film)|Palooka]]'' (1934) - Slats (uncredited)\n* ''[[Cheaters (1934 film)|Cheaters]]'' (1934) - Detective Sweeney\n* ''[[Half a Sinner (1934 film)|Half a Sinner]]'' (1934) - 'Bull' Moran\n* ''[[Here Comes the Navy]]'' (1934) - Dance-Floor Manager\n* ''[[Romance in the Rain (film)|Romance in the Rain]]'' (1934) - Panya Mankiewicz\n* ''[[Thunder Over Texas]]'' (1934) - Ted Wright\n* ''[[Flirtation Walk]]'' (1934) - 'Sleepy'\n* ''[[Cowboy Holiday]]'' (1934) - Buck Sawyer\n* ''[[The Silver Streak]]'' (1934) - Higgins\n* ''[[Big Boy Rides Again]]'' (1935) - Tom Duncan\n* ''[[Private Worlds]]'' (1935) - Jerry\n* ''[[One in a Million (1934 film)|One in a Million]]'' (1935) - Spike McGafferty\n* ''[[Village Tale]]'' (1935) - Ben Roberts\n* ''[[The Glass Key (1935 film)|The Glass Key]]'' (1935) - Jeff\n* ''[[Society Fever]]'' (1935) - Edgar Prouty\n* ''Danger Trails'' (1935) - Bob Wilson\n* ''[[Here Comes Cookie]]'' (1935) - Big Boy\n* ''[[Powdersmoke Range]]'' (1935) - Lullaby Joslin\n* ''Gun Play'' (1935) - Bill Williams\n* ''[[The Law of 45's]]'' (1935) - Tucson Smith\n* ''[[Miss Pacific Fleet]]'' (1935) - Nicholas 'Nick' - Annie's Boyfriend\n* ''[[The Littlest Rebel]]'' (1935) - Sgt. Dudley\n* ''[[Muss 'em Up]]'' (1936) - 'Red' Cable\n* ''[[Kelly the Second]]'' (1936) - Cecil Callahan\n* ''[[Grand Jury (1936 film)|Grand Jury]]'' (1936) - Joseph Britt\n* ''[[The Vigilantes Are Coming]]'' (1936, Serial) - Salvation\n* ''[[The Big Game (1936 film)|The Big Game]]'' (1936) - Pete Jenkins\n* ''[[End of the Trail (1936 film)|End of the Trail]]'' (1936) - Bob Hildreth\n* ''[[North of Nome (1936 film)|North of Nome]]'' (1936) - Haage\n* ''[[Career Woman (film)|Career Woman]]'' (1936) - Bede Sanders\n* ''[[You Only Live Once (1937 film)|You Only Live Once]]'' (1937) - Roger\n* ''[[Don't Tell the Wife]]'' (1937) - Lazarus Hubert Gregory 'Cupid' Dougal\n* ''[[A Star Is Born (1937 film)|A Star Is Born]]'' (1937) - Posture Coach\n* ''[[Dangerous Holiday]]'' (1937) - Duke Edward